<i>The True State of the Planet</i>, chapter 2.<p>

<A NAME="12"></A><sup>12</sup> &#147;Aquaculture Production, World,&#148; in <i>The True State
of the Planet, </i>pp. 424-5.<p>

<A NAME="13"></A><sup>13</sup> Indur Goklany, &#147;Richer Is Cleaner,&#148; in <i>The True
State of the Planet</i>, chapter 10; see also, Aaron Wildavsky, <i>Searching
for Safety</i> (New Brunswick: Transaction Books, 1988).
</DL>
</td></tr></table>
