<H1>SET YOUR VCRs!</H1>
<H3>Fred and Fran Smith to Guest Host NET's "Mitchells in the Morning"</H3>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
                             

<P>CEI is pleased to announce that <A HREF="fred.html">Fred</A> and Fran Smith will guest Co-host the National Empowerment TV show "Mitchells in the Morning" April 15-17.

<DL><DL><DD>
     <P><B>WHAT:</B> NET's "Mitchells in the Morning"

     <P><B>WHEN:</B> Monday, April 15-Wednesday, April 17 8:00 AM-9:00 AM

     <P><B>WHERE:</B> National Empowerment Television (Check your local listings)
</DL></DL>

<P>Please tune in and see Fred and Fran tackle the issues of the day as well as interview guests such as noted author and radio commentator, Armstrong Williams.  You can call in with questions and
comments as well (the phone number will be shown on screen).


<CENTER>
<P>For more information, call Greg Smith at (202) 331-1010.
</CENTER>

<P>

