<TITLE>CEI: Public in Dark about Alcohol and Heart Disease</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="000000" LINK="009900" VLINK="000099">
<BR>

<table border=1><tr>
<td><img src="/images/death.gif" height=75 width=75><A HREF="/fmlp.html"><img src="/images/deathby.gif" height=75 width=275 border=0></A></td></tr></table>
