<B>The Greening of Trade Policy: "Sustainable Development" and Global Trade</B><BR>
by James M. Sheehan<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<P>

<A NAME="151"></A><sup>151</sup> See Lallas, Esty, and van Hoogstraten, pp. 324, 332;
and
<i>World Resources 1994-95</i>, pp. 224-225.<p>
<A NAME="152"></A><sup>152</sup> Excerpted in Pearson and Repetto, p. 87.<p>
