<A NAME="12"></A><sup>12</sup> See, for example, Ralph Keeney,&#148;Morality Risks Induced by
Economic Expenditures,&#148;<i>Risk Analysis</i>, Vol. 10, No. 1, 1990, pp.
147-159.<p>

<A NAME="13"></A><sup>13</sup> Thomas D. Hopkins,&#148;Prepared Statement of Thomas D.
Hopkins:Rochester Institute of Technology, Rochester, New York Before The House
Government Reform and Oversight Committee, National Economic Growth, Natural
Resources and Regulatory Affairs Subcommittee,&#148; May 16, 1996.

